titleInfo.title: Hypergeometric representation of a four-loop vacuum bubble

mods.abstract: In this article, we present a new analytic result for a certain single-mass- scale four-loop vacuum (bubble) integral. We also discuss its systematic c-expansion in d = 4-2 is an element of as well as d = 3-2 is an element of dimensions, the coefficients of which are expressible in terms of harmonic sums at infinity.
